<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />For my life is weary with sorrow</para>

<para style="q1">and my years with groaning.</para>

<para style="q1">My strength fails because of my sin,</para>

<para style="q1">and my bones are wasting away.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />Because of all my enemies, people disdain me;</para>

<para style="q1">my neighbors are appalled at my situation,</para>

<para style="q1">and those who know me are horrified.</para>

<para style="q1">Those who see me in the street run from me.</para>
